name: Diff

types.name: Change
types.comment: This describes how each line has changed and also contains its value.

values.name: diff
values.comment:
Compares general lists.

```
diff [1, 3] [2, 3] == [Removed 1, Added 2, NoChange 3] -- True
```
values.type: List a -> List a -> List (Diff.Change a)

values.name: diffLines
values.comment:
Compares two text.

Giving the following text

```
a = """aaa
bbb
ddd"""

b = """zzz
aaa
ccc
ddd"""
```

results in

```
[ Added "zzz"
, NoChange "aaa"
, Removed "bbb"
, Added "ccc"
, NoChange "ddd"
]
```

.
